<plot>In Mexico the journalist Marquez delivers two Super8 videos and a priceless Egyptian statuette to an Italian Secret Service agent. Both the documents are strictly concerning the diabolic criminal boss Stefano Sensini. Sensini is a legendary figure, famous for his cruelty and intelligence, and for his interest for the artistic world and for archaeological founds. So the agent goes back to Rome with the received objects and, investigating, he understands their importance : they are essential to demonstrate Sensini's crimes once and for all. He is even pushed to apply for the help of a shady archaeologist and of a private detective, who almost caught the boss in the past. So Sensini is forced to intervene, bringing all the characters to a reciprocal fight : someone with the aim of belonging the precious material, someone else to finally stop the boss. Everything will be arranged by a final tour-de-force, when some shadows from the past will be back to decide the present's fate.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?421398</url></doc>
